# Trivy vulnerability ignore file
# Format: one CVE-ID or GHSA-ID per line, optionally followed by an expiry date
# Example:
#   CVE-2023-12345
#   GHSA-xxxx-yyyy-zzzz until:2026-06-01
#
# All entries below are for CVEs that are UNFIXED in Debian 13 Trixie
# (python:3.13-slim base image) with no fix available via apt-get upgrade.
# They are accepted risks, reviewed 2026-04-13. Expiry 2027-07-01 forces
# re-evaluation; remove each entry once Debian ships a patched package.

